# Pitstop dataset CSVs are the SOURCE OF TRUTH for the course/base join chain
# (Courses -> CourseStops -> BaseLatLon). Canonical form is UTF-8 no BOM, LF.
#
# This repo runs with core.autocrlf=true, which would rewrite these to CRLF in
# the working tree on every checkout. The loaders tolerate CRLF (they split on
# /\r?\n/), but the canonical form is LF — pin it so the files on disk match the
# schema they're documented to have, and so diffs stay clean.
*.csv text eol=lf

# Excel workbooks are binary — never line-ending-converted, never diffed as text.
*.xlsx binary
